I/HTMLPictureElement\"><code>HTMLPictureElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLPreElement\"><code>HTMLPreElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLProgressElement\"><code>HTMLProgressElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLQuoteElement\"><code>HTMLQuoteElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLScriptElement\"><code>HTMLScriptElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSelectElement\"><code>HTMLSelectElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement\"><code>HTMLShadowElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSourceElement\"><code>HTMLSourceElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement\"><code>HTMLStyleElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCaptionElement\"><code>HTMLTableCaptionElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCellElement\"><code>HTMLTableCellElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableColElement\"><code>HTMLTableColElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement\"><code>HTMLTableElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableRowElement\"><code>HTMLTableRowElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableSectionElement\"><code>HTMLTableSectionElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTextAreaElement\"><code>HTMLTextAreaElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTimeElement\"><code>HTMLTimeElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTitleElement\"><code>HTMLTitleElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTrackElement\"><code>HTMLTrackElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die <strong><code>HTMLCollection</code></strong> repräsentiert eine generische Sammlung (Array-ähnliches Objekt) an Elementen (in Dokumentreihenfolge) und bietet Methoden und Eigenschaften zur Auswahl dieser aus einer Liste an.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\"><strong>Notiz:</strong> Diese Schnittstelle wird aus historischen Gründen <code>HTMLCollection</code> genannt (vor DOM4 konnten Sammlungen, die diese Schnittstelle implementierten, nur HTML-Elemente als Einträge haben).</div>\n\n<p>Eine <code>HTMLCollection</code> in der HTML DOM ist live; sie wird automatisch aktualisiert, wenn das zugrundeliegende Dokument verändert wird.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlcollection.length_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection/length\"><code>HTMLCollection.length</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Gibt die Anzahl der Elemente in der Auflistung zurück.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methoden","title":"Methoden","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlcollection.item_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection/item\"><code>HTMLCollection.item()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Gibt den spezifischen Knoten am angegebenen nullbasierten <code>index</code> in die Liste zurück.<br>\n Gibt <code>null</code> zurück, wenn der <code>index</code> außerhalb des Bereichs ist.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcollection.nameditem_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection/namedItem\"><code>HTMLCollection.namedItem()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Gibt den spezifischen Knoten, dessen ID oder alternativ dessen Name auf die Zeichenkette (spezifiziert durch <code>name</code>) passt, zurück. Die Übereinstimmung des Namens wird nur als letzte Möglichkeit, nur in HTML, und nur, wenn das referenzierte Element das <code>name</code> Attribut unterstützt, durchgeführt.<br>\n Gibt <code>null</code> zurück, wenn kein Code des angegebenen Namens existiert.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"verwendung_in_javascript","title":"Verwendung in JavaScript","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>HTMLCollection</code> setzt auch seine Member direkt als Eigenschaften von <code>name</code> und <code>index</code>. HTML&nbsp;IDs können Doppelpunkte und Punkte als gültige Zeichen beinhalten, was das Verwenden von Klammern für den Zugriff auf Eigenschaften erfordert. Derzeit erkennt <code>HTMLCollections </code>rein numerische IDs nicht, da sie einen Konflikt mit dem Array-ähnlichen Zugriff verursachen würden, obwohl HTML5 dies erlaubt.</p>\n\n<p>Zum Beispiel, unter der Annahme, dass es ein <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> Element im Dokument und die <code>id</code> <code>\"myForm\"</code> ist:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> elem1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> elem2<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// document.forms ist eine HTMLCollection</span>\n\nelem1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>forms<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nelem2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>forms<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>elem1 <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> elem2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// zeigt: \"true\"</span>\n\nelem1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>forms<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>myForm<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nelem2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>forms<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">namedItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myForm\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>elem1 <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> elem2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// zeigt: \"true\"</span>\n\nelem1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>forms<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"bennantes.Element.mit.Punkten\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_kompatibilität","title":"Browser Kompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Verschiedene Browser verhalten sich unterschiedlich, wenn es mehr als ein Element gibt, das auf die Zeichenkette passt, die als ein index (oder <code>namedItem</code>s Argument) verwendet wird. Firefox 8 verhält sich wie in DOM 2 and DOM4 angegeben, und gibt das erste passende Element zurück. WebKit Browser und Internet Explorer geben in diesem Fall eine andere <code>HTMLCollection</code> und Opera eine <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> aller passenden Elemente zurück.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikation","title":"Spezifikation","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-HTML/html.html#ID-75708506\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 HTML, Section 1.4, Miscellaneous Object Definitions</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/domcore/#interface-htmlcollection\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM4: HTMLCollection</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormControlsCollection\"><code>HTMLFormControlsCollection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLOptionsCollection\"><code>HTMLOptionsCollection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"},{"text":"Methoden","id":"methoden"},{"text":"Verwendung in JavaScript","id":"verwendung_in_javascript"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"},{"text":"Spezifikation","id":"spezifikation"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die HTMLCollection repräsentiert eine generische Sammlung (Array-ähnliches Objekt) an Elementen (in Dokumentreihenfolge) und bietet Methoden und Eigenschaften zur Auswahl dieser aus einer Liste an.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLCollection","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLCollection","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"HTMLCollection","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLCollection","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTMLCollection","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"HTMLCollection","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"HTMLCollection","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTMLCollection","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"HTMLCollection","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/htmlcollection","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/htmlcollection/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection","title":"HTMLCollection"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLCollection - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}